1. What is the advantage of using reactive components in screen flows?
Ans : C. Components react to changes in other components on the same screen in real time.

2. What is the first step to provide mobile users the same experience as desktop users for Dynamic Forms?
Ans : B. Enable Dynamic Forms on Mobile.

3. Which feature allows customization of knowledge content visibility rules?
Ans : A. Article Personalization

4. Screen flow reactivity allows admins to:
Ans : C. Use the ADDMONTHS formula operator to perform real-time logic.

5. The Lightning Article Editor and Article Personalization:
Ans : B. Allows admins to choose which parts of the articles users can see.
